    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夢想和惡夢只有一線之隔…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《非常糟糕的夢》是一種緊張而艱鉅的體驗，會考驗您的神經。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/92a9f18554850fc1d3fe0ceaed397e86.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/92a9f18554850fc1d3fe0ceaed397e86.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/92a9f18554850fc1d3fe0ceaed397e86.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘記您自以為了解的有關恐怖遊戲的一切，因為《非常糟糕的夢》超越了遊戲體驗的界限。由法國獨立工作室開發的《Very Bad Dreams》不僅僅是一款遊戲。這是一種非凡的沉浸式體驗，你的生存取決於真實的行動。你需要本能地做出反應才能在這個可怕的世界中生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受你的打擊力量的衝擊力，當你被敵人擊中或心跳加速時，感受你頭部的震動，用你真實的手勢奔跑和跳躍，用雙手抱住你的頭，以免發瘋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/321512f9156f778f7e232cab7e410010.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/321512f9156f778f7e232cab7e410010.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/321512f9156f778f7e232cab7e410010.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如此多的新遊戲元素會給你一種從未做過同樣事情的印象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你喜歡尋找無盡的戰利品嗎？嘗試數百種武器和藥水組合？花幾個小時在庫存上？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《非常糟糕的夢》不適合你……這裡只有一個字警告，害怕……非常害怕，無論你有槍、球棒還是刀，最好的辦法就是逃跑，不要陷入瘋狂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/cf15a9765797a7c3faef332fd912c2f4.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/cf15a9765797a7c3faef332fd912c2f4.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/cf15a9765797a7c3faef332fd912c2f4.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您在田園詩般的海灘上醒來，腳踩在白色的沙灘上，當太陽落在地平線上時，微風徐徐。在這段悠閒的散步中，地獄之門向你敞開。在你的驕傲驅使下，你認為你可以跨越它們而不必承受後果，但很快你發現自己的完美夢想變成了一場令人壓抑的噩夢，沒有出路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/c753c44b877bb82e966d7784e39cd51b.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/c753c44b877bb82e966d7784e39cd51b.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/c753c44b877bb82e966d7784e39cd51b.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在瘋狂的氛圍中為生存而戰，每走一步都會增加焦慮，面對成群的殭屍，解決謎題或尋找最佳的藏身之處。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對於你們當中最勇敢的人來說，準備好體驗非凡的沉浸式體驗吧，在這裡恐怖變得栩栩如生，每一刻都可以決定你們的命運。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/0832ade71a879019544ec4d2dc53bf08.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/0832ade71a879019544ec4d2dc53bf08.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/0832ade71a879019544ec4d2dc53bf08.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面對內心的惡魔，戰勝最深的恐懼。但請記住，永遠、永遠不要屈服於瘋狂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你敢跳入惡夢的無盡深淵嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我們會警告你...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/7803a72bde11a9171488f8e23275bfc4.poster.avif?t=1734650348\" width=542 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/7803a72bde11a9171488f8e23275bfc4.webm?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331260/extras/7803a72bde11a9171488f8e23275bfc4.mp4?t=1734650348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
